title: Bundle Monster 66 Professional Color Lip Gloss Lipstick Makeup Cosmetic Palette
description: Check out this great make up deal, 66 Color Lip Gloss/Lipstick palette. This set is brand new in box and comes in our branded matte black case. The set features a nice mixture of matte and glossy lip colors - including: natural, neutral colors to warm and cool colors - a great palette for any type of look you are going for. Some of the colors have glitter inside for extra shimmer. This palette can be used for daytime and night-time looks and even great for special occassions like weddings, parties and costuming. Each of the 66 lip gloss pots are about 1.8 cm diameter and is perfect for traveling in its compact, lightweight case. Palette Dimension: 23cm x 15.3 cm x .6 cm. NOTE: Due to differences between monitor displays, actual color may vary slightly from image. Keep away from fire and open flames. Keep out of reach of children - adult supervision required.
